a segregationist who has stood trial twice 
in the 1963 ambush slaying of civil rights leader medgar evers 
faces a third trial after being indicted on new evidence 
byron de la beckwith 70 of signal mountain tenn is charged 
with murder in the shooting death of evers field secretary for the 
