i think trump keating and the boys were a reflection of what 
we were taken to a much larger level sterner said its 
easier to blame them bums 
the question for 1991 is not whos to blame but where will it 
end whats going to happen to pull the economy out of its nose 
dive 
amid the gloom some suggest the comparisons to the 30s are 
misplaced 
for one thing the economy is more diversified and efficient 
than it was 60 years ago strengthened by an array of systems to 
transmit goods services knowledge and ideas that are the envy of 
the world 
