examination of its loan portfolio by the us office of the 
comptroller of the currency a comptroller spokeswoman said banking 
audits are confidential and the results wont be released 
the company said it would discuss the developments in greater 
detail following release of its yearend results in midjanuary 
based in new york citicorp is the nations leading banking company 
with assets exceeding 2306 billion 
the feds cut in the discount rate generally precedes a 
reduction in a banks prime rate an important rate that is often a 
benchmark for a range of other consumer loan rates such as 
mortgages norwest bank of minneapolis minn cut its prime rate 
percent late tuesday to 975 percent 
norwest president james r campbell said the company is the 
first major us bank to lower their rate 
norwest bank is the largest banking affiliate of norwest 
corporation a financial services organization with 296 billion 
in assets three small banks cut their prime rates on dec 7 after 
the fed dropped to 7 percent the rate charges for federal funds 
the rate which banks charge each other for overnight loans 
how quickly other banks follow and cut their prime rates is open 
to speculation analysts said 
the abas chessen said banks will take slow measured steps in 
lowering their prime rate theres a lot of uncertainty in the 
market and they will react cautiously 
