chip which is used in powerful personal computers and midrange 
machines but it is up to three times faster the san francisco 
chronicle reported tuesday 
but the chip may operate too quickly for the way most computers 
are currently designed analysts and competitors say they add that 
intels factories may not be able to produce the chip in volume for 
at least three years 
 
